graph LR
    RhodsOp[rhods-operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    RhodsOp -->|platform runtime| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+<br/>OpenShift 4.12+]
    RhodsOp -->|model serving<br/>traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Operator<br/>Required for KServe]
    RhodsOp -->|autoscaling<br/>serverless| Serverless[Serverless Operator<br/>Knative Serving<br/>Required for KServe]
    RhodsOp -->|model serving<br/>authentication| Authorino[Authorino Operator<br/>Required for KServe auth]
    RhodsOp -.->|certificate mgmt<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    RhodsOp -.->|monitoring<br/>optional| PromOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>Optional]
    RhodsOp -.->|console integration<br/>optional| Console[OpenShift Console 4.12+<br/>ConsoleLinks, QuickStarts]

    %% Component Deployments (Internal ODH)
    RhodsOp -->|deploys CRDs<br/>manages UI| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>OdhApplication, OdhDocument]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests<br/>configures| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Multi-model serving]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys CRDs| DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>DataSciencePipelinesApplication]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>Distributed workloads]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>Ray clusters]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| Training[Training Operator<br/>Kubeflow Training]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job queueing]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys service| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model metadata]
    RhodsOp -->|deploys manifests| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator<br/>Model monitoring]

    %% External Service Dependencies
    RhodsOp -->|downloads manifests| GitHub[github.com<br/>HTTPS/443]
    RhodsOp -->|pulls images| QuayIO[quay.io<br/>HTTPS/443]
    RhodsOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>HTTPS/6443]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|UI management| RhodsOp
    DSP -.->|pipeline deploy| KServe

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| RhodsOp

